title: SkypeSetup_2015
description:
Enjoy Modern new Skype for Windows. Here are some wonderful tasks that you can perform:
Chat with every day using free instant messaging.
Share photos and watch aside by side within chat directly.
Enjoy your family come together through free group video call.
Instead of between the contacts and messages, or use Monday at the same time.
Wage low-cost calls and sent SMS messages to mobile phones and land lines.
All you need to start is Microsoft Windows XP with SP3 or Vista or 7 or 8 or 8.1 web camera for video calls and a microphone.
